## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Local Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/alert-after-pro/alert-after-pro
cd alert-after-pro
pip install -e .
```

### Testing

```bash
# Install with dev dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Test specific notifier
aa --test
```

